Utterances.UttText: Subj  Gerry Cage is a 56yo woman with PMHx HTN who reports episode of recent chest pain 3 days ago.

Phrases.PhraseText: episode of recent chest pain 3 days ago.

Utterances.UttText: States that she was carrying groceries across a parking lot when she felt a heavy/deep ache in her chest.

Phrases.PhraseText: carrying groceries across a parking lot
a heavy/deep ache in her chest.

Utterances.UttText: The pain subsided with 5-10 mins of rest once she got to her car.
She has never experienced chest pain like this before.

Phrases.PhraseText: never experienced chest pain like this before.

Utterances.UttText: States she does not know if she has had cholesterol checked.
Denies swelling in hands or feet.
Does not get much regular exercise, but has not noticed any changes in her ability to walk her dog short distances.
